snippet.title: Moundville Factory Lost Tape 89 Teaser Trailer - Urbex "The Lost Tapes" Series
snippet.description:
Moundville Factory Lost Tape 89 - The second entry in "The Lost Tapes Series". Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/moundville-factory-lost-tape-89

Story: Explore Moundville factory a former electronics production building which was later sold to another company and made into a water treatment facility. Rumors of the past say the building was not just sold though, but that something sinister haunts these grounds.

You've survived the "Incident Tapes" Series, now it's time to put your urban exploration skills and sanity to the ultimate test.

VHS Urbex Found Footage "The Lost Tapes" Series will contain:
 Strongford Penitentiary Lost tape 91 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/strongford-penitentiary-lost-tape-91
 Moundville Factory Lost Tape 89 - Paid - Out now! https://azagamestudio.itch.io/moundville-factory-lost-tape-89
 Durium Hospital Lost Tape 95 - Paid - Coming soon

Moundville Factory Lost Tape 89 is a VHS Urban Exploration Found Footage horror title with emphasis on atmosphere, unpredictability, realism and a non-linear design with multiple endings and outcomes.
